---
title: Bell Pepper & Edamame Lo Mein with Carrots, Peanuts & Wonton Strips
description: This bold, savory stir-fry features tender lo mein noodles, crisp-tender bell pepper, and hearty edamame all tossed in a savory-sweet chili-soy glaze. Finished with crunchy peanuts, crispy wonton strips, and a drizzle of Sriracha for extra kick, this dish brings a fusion of textures and flavors to every bite!
